              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The target was manufactured from both metallic",
                "  hafnium of natural isotopic composition, and from",
                "  enriched powdered hafnium.",
                " At EN-MAX = 55 MeV, the irradiations were performed",
                "  using three targets:",
                "  - natural Hf target in the form of a 4.0 x 4.0 x",
                "    0.7 mm rectangular strip of 180 mg;",
                "  - enriched 179HfO2 powder (73.7% of 179Hf), poured",
                "    into a 0.8 x 0.9 x 0.3 cm polyethylene bag of",
                "    350 mg;",
                "  - enriched 180HfO2 powder (94.3% of 180Hf), poured",
                "    into a 1.0 x 1.0 x 0.3 cm polyethylene bag of",
                "    390 mg."
              ]
            }
